1. *Tražimo* nova rešenja za naš problem. (We are looking for new solutions for our problem.)
2. *Tražimo* da nam to bude odmah dostupno. (We are asking for it to be available to us immediately.)
3. Oni *traže* da se odgovori daju što pre. (They are asking for answers to be given as soon as possible.)
4. Mi *tražimo* da nam se pruži pomoć. (We are requesting for assistance to be provided to us.)
5. *Tražili* smo da nam se obezbedi bolji uslovi. (We asked for better conditions to be secured for us.)